<main class="margin-top-xl margin-bottom-xl">
    <div class="container max-width-xs">
                                <div class="alert margin-bottom-sm alert--error js-alert--error" role="alert">
            <div class="alert__content">
                <div class="text-component">
                    <!--<p><strong>Error:</strong> email or password not valid.</p>-->
                    <p>⚠️ <strong>Warning:</strong> <mark>Did you confirmed your email address</mark> by clicking on the link in the email we sent you?</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="margin-bottom-sm">
            <h1>Log in</h1>
            <p class="margin-top-xxxs">or <a class="color-secondary" href="sign-up">create an account</a></p>
        </div>
        <form method="post" class="js-login-form">
            <input type="hidden" value="/account/account-settings" class="js-login-redirect">
            <input name="csrf_token" value="1e4b82ad360d50a0bcde1ebd149298950f95123c3e621e6da4437d095a2a22d23250a1" type="hidden">
            <div class="margin-bottom-sm js-signup-form__input-wrapper">
                <label class="form-label" for="loginEmail">Email <span class="form-label__error">- Required</span><span class="form-label__error">- Wrong format</span><span class="form-label__error">- address Invalid</span></label></label>
                <input class="form-control width-100%" type="email" name="loginEmail" id="loginEmail" maxlength="60" required>
            </div>
            <div class="margin-bottom-sm js-signup-form__input-wrapper">
                <label class="form-label" for="loginPassword">Password <span class="form-label__error">- Required</span></label>
                <div class="password js-password">
                    <input class="form-control width-100% password__input js-password__input" type="password" name="loginPassword" id="loginPassword" minlength="6" maxlength="20" required>
                    <button class="password__btn flex flex-center js-password__btn" aria-hidden="true">
                        <span class="password__btn-label" title="Show Password">Show</span>
                        <span class="password__btn-label" title="Hide Password">Hide</span>
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between flex-wrap flex-gap-xs items-center">
                <a class="color-secondary" href="lost-password">Lost your password?</a>
                <button class="btn btn--primary btn--md btn--preserve-width js-login-form__submit">
                    <span class="btn__content-a">
                        Login </span>
                    <span class="btn__content-b">
                        <svg class="icon icon--md icon--is-spinning" viewBox="0 0 32 32">
                            <path d="M16,32A16,16,0,1,1,32,16,16.019,16.019,0,0,1,16,32ZM16,4A12,12,0,1,0,28,16,12.013,12.013,0,0,0,16,4Z" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.4"></path>
                            <path d="M32,16H28A12.013,12.013,0,0,0,16,4V0A16.019,16.019,0,0,1,32,16Z" fill="currentColor"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </span>
                </button>
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>
</main>






<section class="thank-you padding-top-xl padding-top-md@lg margin-bottom-xl">
    <blockquote class="position-relative z-index-1 bg-contrast-lower text-center padding-y-xl">
        <div class="container max-width-adaptive-md">
            <div class="margin-bottom-md">
                <svg class="icon icon--xl color-contrast-low" aria-hidden="true" viewBox="0 0 64 64">
                    <polygon fill="currentColor" points="2 36 17 2 26 2 15 36 26 36 26 62 2 62 2 36"></polygon>
                    <polygon fill="currentColor" points="38 36 53 2 62 2 51 36 62 36 62 62 38 62 38 36"></polygon>
                </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="text-component">
                <p class="text-lg">I am incredibly grateful for immooff.net, as it has significantly enhanced my automotive repair business. With the site's extensive collection of files, software, and guides for immobilizer removal, ECU repair, and key replacement, I can confidently find the solutions I need to work more efficiently than ever before. Immensely impressive work!</p>
            </div>
            <footer class="margin-top-lg">— David Cadogan</footer>
        </div>
    </blockquote>
</section>
